    {
      "q": "How do upgrades work?",
      "a": "Upgrade anytime; we prorate the change and unlock features immediately. Downgrades apply at the next billing cycle."
    },
    {
      "q": "What counts as a 'household' and 'collaborator'?",
      "a": "A household is one family unit in your workspace. Collaborators are people you invite—spouse/partner, adult children, or trusted pros."
    },
    {
      "q": "Bank connections & data syncing?",
      "a": "Premium and Pro support secure bank connections for net worth and cashflow. You control what's linked and can disconnect anytime."
    },
    {
      "q": "Storage & document limits?",
      "a": "Free includes 10 uploads total. Premium and Pro include expanded storage and exports. Large or regulated archives are available for RIAs."
    },
    {
      "q": "Is my data private?",
      "a": "Yes. You control sharing. We provide encrypted storage, role-based access, and audit receipts on supported plans."
